OL,5, Livestock farms in England polluted    
OL,6, rivers 300 times last year, causing 20 
OL,7, major incidents, according to the      
OL,8, latest government figures.             
OL,10,FYet only six farms were prosecuted in  
OL,11,F2021, with the Environment Agency      
OL,12,Fgiving out warning letters instead.    
OL,14,FThe dairy industry - mostly thanks to  
OL,15,Fthe waste its millions of cows produce 
OL,16,F- is the worst environmental offender, 
OL,17,Flinked to half of all farm pollution.  
OL,19,FThe government said prosecution was a  
OL,20,Flast resort for persistent offenders.  
